---
title: Shrimp and Chorizo Paella with Smoked Paprika, Tomato, and Peas
description: Paella, the national dish of Spain, is famous for its socarrat, the crispy crust that develops on the bottom of the pan. This version is flavored with smoky chorizo and paprika for major depth of flavor
